    public interface CyPhyIntrospectionCI
extends fr.sorbonne_u.components.reflection.interfaces.IntrospectionCI
    The interface CyPhyIntrospectionCI extends the standard BCM introspection interface with methods regarding the cyber-physical part of cy-phy components.
